{
  "version": 1,
  "report_html_template": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<!-- Meeting report template — rendered server-side by GhostPour -->\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f2f2ee;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;\">\n\n<div style=\"max-width:620px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;\">\n  <!-- CTA OVERLAY — sample-report upsell banner -->\n  <div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a1a 0%,#3a1f5c 50%,#0f3460 100%);padding:18px 24px;border-bottom:2px solid #fbbf24;\">\n    <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n      <tr valign=\"middle\">\n        <td>\n          <div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:#fbbf24;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:5px;\">{{cta_eyebrow}}</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:3px;\">{{cta_headline}}</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size:11.5px;color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.45;\">{{cta_body}}</div>\n        </td>\n        <td style=\"text-align:right;width:140px;vertical-align:middle;padding-left:10px;\">\n          <a href=\"#\" data-action=\"open_paywall\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffffff 0%,#f0f0f0 100%);color:#1a1a1a;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;padding:11px 18px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.02em;white-space:nowrap;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\">{{cta_button_text}}</a>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n\n  <!-- Masthead — project name + report number -->\n  \n  <div style=\"padding:8px 32px;background:#f5f5f2;border-bottom:1px solid #ebebeb;\">\n    <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n      <td style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:#888;\">Project <span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:13px;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;\">All Bravo Mark</span></td>\n      <td style=\"text-align:right;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#aaa;\">Meeting Report</td>\n    </tr></table>\n  </div>\n  \n\n  <!-- Top bar -->\n  <div style=\"background:#1a1a1a;padding:12px 32px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#ffffff;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:6px;\">Technical Working Session</div>\n    <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n      <td style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;font-family:monospace;text-align:left;\">April 30, 2026</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;font-family:monospace;text-align:center;\">8:59 AM CDT</td>\n      <td style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;font-family:monospace;text-align:right;\">1h 39m</td>\n    </tr></table>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Header -->\n  <div style=\"padding:28px 32px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid #ebebeb;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:12px;\">Agent context configuration and SDK integration troubleshooting</div>\n\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;\">The team debugged agent context issues in the SDK integration, discovering that context was being sent as empty due to agent access restrictions and configuration mismatches. After opening agent access to all users and confirming the correct agent IDs across environments, the team verified the fix works in sandbox and QA environments. Testing will continue next week after the holiday.</div>\n\n    <!-- Attendees -->\n    <div style=\"margin-top:14px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid #f0f0ec;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:8px;\">Identified speakers</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#555;line-height:1.8;\">\n        <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Ina</span> <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Christian</span> <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Lauren</span> <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Brendan</span> <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Madison</span> <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Ethan</span> <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Gavin</span> <span style=\"background:#f0f0ec;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;margin-right:4px;margin-bottom:4px;display:inline-block;\">Abraham</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Stoplight + Sentiment -->\n    <div style=\"margin-top:14px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid #f0f0ec;\">\n\n      <!-- Stoplight -->\n      <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-bottom:14px;padding-bottom:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0ec;\"><tr valign=\"middle\">\n        <td style=\"padding-right:16px;\">\n          <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n            <!-- Four circles: light up the one matching stoplight.color, others are #e0e0db -->\n            <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td width=\"18\" height=\"18\" bgcolor=\"#e0e0db\" style=\"border-radius:9px;width:18px;height:18px;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td></tr>\n            <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td width=\"18\" height=\"18\" bgcolor=\"#e0e0db\" style=\"border-radius:9px;width:18px;height:18px;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td></tr>\n            <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom:4px;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td width=\"18\" height=\"18\" bgcolor=\"#FFD54F\" style=\"border-radius:9px;width:18px;height:18px;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td></tr>\n            <tr><td align=\"center\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td width=\"18\" height=\"18\" bgcolor=\"#e0e0db\" style=\"border-radius:9px;width:18px;height:18px;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td></tr>\n          </table>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#7D6608;margin-bottom:3px;\">Major issue resolved pending verification</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#888;line-height:1.6;\">The team identified and fixed a critical agent context bug by updating agent access permissions and verifying configuration. Testing is ongoing but blocked until next week due to holiday, leaving some verification work incomplete.</div>\n        </td>\n      </tr></table>\n\n      <!-- Sentiment Score + Label -->\n      <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr valign=\"middle\">\n        <td style=\"padding-right:12px;\">\n          <div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n            <div style=\"background:#FFFDE7;border-radius:50%;width:44px;height:44px;text-align:center;line-height:44px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#7D6608;margin:0 auto;\">68</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#7D6608;margin-top:3px;\">Sentiment</div>\n          </div>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:2px;\">Focused and collaborative problem solving</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#888;line-height:1.5;\">The meeting demonstrated strong technical collaboration with team members systematically debugging a complex configuration issue. While there were moments of tension as the root cause was uncovered, the overall tone was problem-focused and solutions-oriented.</div>\n        </td>\n      </tr></table>\n\n      <!-- Sentiment Arc (progressive disclosure via <details>, email-safe) -->\n      <details style=\"margin-top:12px;\">\n        <summary style=\"font-size:11px;color:#7D6608;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:underline;list-style:none;\">View sentiment arc</summary>\n        <div style=\"padding:12px 14px;background:#fafaf8;border:1px solid #e8e8e4;border-radius:4px;margin-top:8px;\">\n          <div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:10px;\">Sentiment arc</div>\n          <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"100%\" style=\"height:48px;\"><tr valign=\"bottom\">\n            <td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#888780\" height=\"32\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#E24B4A\" height=\"28\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#E24B4A\" height=\"24\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#888780\" height=\"35\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#639922\" height=\"38\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#639922\" height=\"42\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#639922\" height=\"45\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#888780\" height=\"44\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#E24B4A\" height=\"40\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#888780\" height=\"38\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#639922\" height=\"42\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td><td style=\"vertical-align:bottom;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td bgcolor=\"#888780\" height=\"36\" style=\"border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table></td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <!-- Legend -->\n          <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;padding-top:8px;border-top:1px solid #f0f0ec;\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"padding-right:14px;white-space:nowrap;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr valign=\"middle\"><td width=\"8\" height=\"8\" bgcolor=\"#639922\" style=\"border-radius:4px;width:8px;height:8px;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"font-size:10px;color:#555;padding-left:5px;\">Confident</td></tr></table></td>\n            <td style=\"padding-right:14px;white-space:nowrap;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr valign=\"middle\"><td width=\"8\" height=\"8\" bgcolor=\"#EF9F27\" style=\"border-radius:4px;width:8px;height:8px;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"font-size:10px;color:#555;padding-left:5px;\">Tense</td></tr></table></td>\n            <td style=\"padding-right:14px;white-space:nowrap;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr valign=\"middle\"><td width=\"8\" height=\"8\" bgcolor=\"#E24B4A\" style=\"border-radius:4px;width:8px;height:8px;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"font-size:10px;color:#555;padding-left:5px;\">Concern</td></tr></table></td>\n            <td style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr valign=\"middle\"><td width=\"8\" height=\"8\" bgcolor=\"#888780\" style=\"border-radius:4px;width:8px;height:8px;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"font-size:10px;color:#555;padding-left:5px;\">Neutral</td></tr></table></td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <div style=\"margin-top:8px;font-size:11px;color:#888;line-height:1.6;\">The meeting started with concern as the team discovered the agent context was being sent as empty, causing SDK integration failures. Tension increased as they explored various potential causes including configuration mismatches and API issues. Confidence grew as Gavin and Abraham systematically debugged the code and discovered the root cause was agent access restrictions. The sentiment peaked when the team successfully opened agent access and verified the fix worked across environments, though it declined slightly as time pressures emerged due to the holiday schedule.</div>\n        </div>\n      </details>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- SECTION: Action Required -->\n  <div style=\"background:#fff8f0;border-top:3px solid #E24B4A;padding:24px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0e8e0;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:16px;\">Action Required</div>\n\n    <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Abraham</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Implement dynamic agent ID retrieval from API instead of hardcoding values in configuration files</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Gavin</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Update agent context implementation to use API response data on initial load</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Brendan</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Provide method signature and API details for retrieving agent configuration dynamically</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Abraham</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Test QA environment configuration after switching agent ID from sandbox to QA value</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Madison</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Continue testing with current fixes in sandbox environment and defer comprehensive testing to next week</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Brendan</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Investigate available APIs for exporting chat logs and phrase logs externally</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Brendan</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Research server-side search functionality for historical data based on ticket ID</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0e0d8;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px 10px 0;width:96px;vertical-align:top;\"><span style=\"background:#1a1a1a;color:#ffffff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap;\">Brendan</span></td><td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;\">Discuss microfront-end-based integration approach for phase 2 planning</td></tr>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- SECTION: Critical Technical Issues -->\n  \n  <div style=\"padding:24px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #ebebeb;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:16px;\">Critical Technical Issue</div>\n\n    <div style=\"border-left:3px solid #E24B4A;background:#fff5f5;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">bug Identified</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Agent context sent as empty to SDK</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">The agent context object was being passed as empty when making API calls to the SDK, preventing proper agent identification and routing. The root cause was traced to limited agent access permissions that prevented the user from accessing the configured agent, causing the system to fall back to an empty context or incorrect default agent. Additionally, the agent ID being hardcoded did not match the actual agent available in the user's workspace.</div><div style=\"margin-top:10px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid #fadddd;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">Position stated</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.6;color:#666;\">Gavin identified the issue through network inspection and code debugging</div></div></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #E24B4A;background:#fff5f5;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">gap Identified</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Hardcoded agent configuration values not parameterized</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">The agent ID, service now app ID, and other configuration values were hardcoded in the application instead of being retrieved dynamically from the backend API. This caused environment-specific mismatches and prevented the application from adapting to different workspace configurations.</div><div style=\"margin-top:10px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid #fadddd;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">Position stated</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.6;color:#666;\">Christian and Abraham emphasized the need to parameterize these values</div></div></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #E24B4A;background:#fff5f5;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">gap Identified</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">No external API for exporting chat logs and history</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">The team identified that there is no exposed API for external consumption to download chat logs, phrase logs, or historical data. Currently, search and filtering only work on locally loaded data, and there is a story in backlog to fetch history from the DV but it is not yet implemented.</div><div style=\"margin-top:10px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid #fadddd;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">Position stated</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.6;color:#666;\">Brendan raised the business requirement for server-side historical search</div></div></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #E24B4A;background:#fff5f5;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">risk Identified</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Potential multi-agent scenario not addressed</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">The current implementation assumes ABM will have only one agent. However, if a user or workspace has access to multiple agents, the system has no mechanism to allow the user to select which agent to use, potentially causing incorrect routing or context confusion.</div><div style=\"margin-top:10px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid #fadddd;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#A32D2D;margin-bottom:4px;\">Position stated</div><div style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.6;color:#666;\">Gavin raised the concern about how to handle multiple agents</div></div></div>\n\n    <!-- Positive Developments (rendered inside same section if they exist) -->\n    <div style=\"border-left:3px solid #4CAF50;background:#f5fbf0;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px;\">New Development</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Agent access issue identified and resolved</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">The team discovered that agent access was restricted to limited users, preventing proper context retrieval. Brendan opened the agent access to all users, which immediately resolved the context visibility issue and allowed proper agent matching across environments.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #4CAF50;background:#f5fbf0;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px;\">New Development</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Configuration correctly applied across sandbox and QA</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">After fixing the agent access, the team verified that different agent IDs are correctly configured for sandbox (3160419B) and QA (999FF4A) environments through the Angular build process that replaces environment configuration files during deployment.</div></div><div style=\"border-left:3px solid #4CAF50;background:#f5fbf0;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><div style=\"font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px;\">New Development</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">SDK integration working correctly after agent context fix</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">Once the agent access was opened and the correct agent ID was being used, the team confirmed that the SDK is receiving the proper context object with all required fields (agent ID, agent name) and routing is working as expected.</div></div>\n  </div>\n  \n\n  <!-- SECTION: Decisions Made -->\n  \n  <div style=\"padding:24px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #ebebeb;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:16px;\">Decisions Made</div>\n\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #e8e8e4;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:10px;\"><div style=\"padding:14px 16px;\"><div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px;\">Agreed</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Open agent access to all users instead of limited users</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">The team decided to change agent access settings from limited users to everyone to prevent context from being sent as empty due to access restrictions. This allows all users to properly access the configured agent and receive correct context in the SDK.</div></div></div><div style=\"border:1px solid #e8e8e4;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:10px;\"><div style=\"padding:14px 16px;\"><div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px;\">Agreed</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Parameterize agent configuration via API instead of hardcoding</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">Rather than continuing with hardcoded agent ID and app ID values in configuration files, the team decided to retrieve these values dynamically from the backend API on application load. This ensures the configuration always matches what is deployed on the backend.</div></div></div><div style=\"border:1px solid #e8e8e4;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:10px;\"><div style=\"padding:14px 16px;\"><div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px;\">Agreed</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Defer further testing to next week</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">Due to holiday schedule, the team decided to continue basic testing with current fixes this week and defer comprehensive testing to Monday when development support is available. This allows validation work to be properly resourced.</div></div></div><div style=\"border:1px solid #e8e8e4;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:10px;\"><div style=\"padding:14px 16px;\"><div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px;\">Agreed</div><div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:6px;\">Explore microfront-end integration for phase 2</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;\">Brendan suggested adopting a microfront-end-based integration approach in phase 2 that would allow picking standalone components and plugging them into applications, potentially reducing complexity around configuration and search features.</div></div></div>\n  </div>\n  \n\n  <!-- SECTION: Open Questions -->\n  \n  <div style=\"padding:24px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #ebebeb;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:16px;\">Open Questions</div>\n\n    <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e8e8e4;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n      <tr style=\"background:#f5f5f2;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e4;\">\n        <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#aaa;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e4;\">Question</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#aaa;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e4;width:30%;\">Owner</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0ec;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.5;\">How should the system handle scenarios where a user has access to multiple agents?</td><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#666;\">Gavin</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0ec;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.5;\">Are the service now app ID and agent environment values still needed in the context, or can they be trimmed since routing is based only on agent ID?</td><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#666;\">Madison</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0ec;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.5;\">What is the best approach for implementing server-side historical data search when users need to search by ticket ID or other criteria?</td><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#666;\">Brendan</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0ec;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.5;\">Can the API for exporting chat logs and phrase logs be exposed for external consumption?</td><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#666;\">Brendan</td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0ec;\"><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#333;line-height:1.5;\">Which feedback loop metrics from the core platform need to be exported to Service Now for reporting?</td><td style=\"padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#666;\">Christian</td></tr>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n  \n\n  <!-- SECTION: AI Queries During Meeting (Progressive Disclosure, email-safe) -->\n\n  <!-- Footer -->\n  <div style=\"padding:20px 32px;background:#f8f8f5;border-top:1px solid #ebebeb;text-align:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#bbb;line-height:1.5;\">Meeting notes powered by <a href=\"https://shouldersurf.com\" style=\"color:#888;text-decoration:underline;\">Shoulder Surf</a></div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
